title: Ivanka Trump, Jared Kushner on Aspen Ski Break Amid Washington Drama
text:
Ivanka Trump, Jared Kushner on Aspen Ski Break Amid Washington Drama By @rebeccaballhaus Mar 23, 2017 5:18 pm ET 
The White House deployed an army of top advisers to President Donald Trump’s meeting Thursday morning with the House Freedom Caucus, many of whom are holdouts on the GOP health law. Missing from that squadron of senior aides: his daughter Ivanka Trump and son-in-law Jared Kushner. During a week in which Mr. Trump has faced […]
